The only real problem I have with these changes is that I'm in Australia. 8pm to me is 8am in the morning in the USA.<br>
Often there aint the numbers on to form up enough groups (holy trinity groups I mean). The bottle neck often being clerics and slowers. I sit lfg not because I'm not wanted but because there aint any spare spots in any viable groups.<br>
